{"tid":58820,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"鳥山明：女兒因為《銀魂》才去看《七龍珠》","createTime":"2016-12-29T06:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T14:24:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50c108a850479ce18bb8f85f1e61b44b7f0ac86e","tid":58820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"說到日本少年漫畫界的至尊級人物，鳥山明絕對能夠當得起一切榮譽。而他創作的《七龍珠》基本上也是每一個動漫迷都曾經看過、或者至少也是聽說過的吧？不過近日，老爺子卻在寫感言的時候感謝《銀魂》，理由居然是「這部作品讓我的女兒去看《七龍珠》了」。 <br />\n<br />\n從網友提供的圖片上可以看到，鳥山明表示：「我的女兒是《銀魂》的超級粉絲。買了一大堆周邊之類的東西。而說到她父親的漫畫則根本沒有興趣，她只喜歡不斷地看《銀魂》。有一次，我發現她罕見地拿著《七龍珠》在看，還以為怎麼了呢，結果她表示只是想看看《銀魂》裡面NETA的原出處而已。空知老師，謝謝你了。」而對此，空知英秋也在下面的評論當中表示：「鳥山明老師，不，應該說您的女兒&hellip;&hellip;亦或者稱呼她為公主？總之真的謝謝了。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.bunnygo.net/images/20161228/20161228005609248.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bunnygo.net%2Fimages%2F20161228%2F20161228005609248.jpg&h=33c698e9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對此，很多網友吐槽說：「老爺子，這是該笑還是該哭&hellip;&hellip;」「其實想想看也很正常啊，《銀魂》畢竟吸引了太多女性關注。如果是兒子的話，估計會在學校裡整天炫耀自己老爸是鳥山明了吧？」「我記得岸本齊史就說過自己的兒子不看《火影》只喜歡《七龍珠》，當漫畫家真心不容易啊。」"},{"pid":"d220faf478c091601a62f69b8d91a1580a8f9c47","tid":58820,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都幾慘"},{"pid":"d21193381f453fc7fb06ab31fc40e4730acfda02","tid":58820,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81195aeb790f909f618aa8f0d0e6135287cca448","tid":58820,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:50:06.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"573b6b9e18f65c524d0b4b7b575a04e2964ccaa8","tid":58820,"uid":46759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"銀魂宇宙第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa834f1e0657c884411cec64df3913fd88bf9af6","tid":58820,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:58:26.000Z","msg":"見到老竇咁柒悶既人 覺得佢畫埋d唔好睇既野"},{"pid":"75e625d6b04f1cc70fac7c4e555869fc322c11f5","tid":58820,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:01:39.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"361ea9858b6f23687158fd6082445238664d0e25","tid":58820,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b874e064f3cb0a7bccce9f5708610d3603ac946","tid":58820,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆龍珠要睇好快就睇晒<br />\n佢個女真係有性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cf94cdad281ff85e9d9ae763590c9f89392c2e","tid":58820,"uid":8575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:21:58.000Z","msg":"林空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea450d4c36ffe9648d26df33b59052bd5dfdb2e3","tid":58820,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:34:15.000Z","msg":"身邊追銀魂嘅囡囡個個都好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0154ec9d5d234e8be26daa68da82e1d53cf4b8c","tid":58820,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"只係睇睇NETA出處咋,真係陰公"},{"pid":"0e24d37e26f23215d78b620516ee04bf0ec935c5","tid":58820,"uid":33376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"Neta即係邊個呀<img src=\"/assets